> Connect your project to any AI. No API key. No copy-paste. Build anything.

**pip install codebridge-mcp**

---

## What is CodeBridge?

CodeBridge is a free tool that connects your local project folder directly to Claude, ChatGPT, or Gemini.

Once connected — the AI reads your files, writes fixes, and runs commands directly in your project. You just talk to it like normal.

No API key. No subscription. No copy-paste. Just your free AI account and your project.

---

## Who is it for?

Developers who cannot afford Claude Code or Codex but still want AI to read and fix their actual project files — not just answer questions in a chat box.

---

## Install

```bash
pip install codebridge-mcp
```

Requires Python 3.8+. No other dependencies.

---

## Run

```bash
# In your project folder
python -m codebridge start
```

